videoSnippet.title: Who Knows What Secrets We'll Uncover | Svidler vs Shankland | Hoogeveen (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Peter Svidler vs Samuel Shankland
Hoogeveen Matches (2018)
25 Oct 2018.
Reti Opening (A06)

1. Nf3 d5 2. e3 Nf6 3. c4 e6 4. Nc3 dxc4 5. Bxc4 a6 6. O-O b5 7. Bb3 Bb7 8. d4 Nbd7 9. Qe2 c5 10. Rd1 Qb8 11. e4 cxd4 12. Nxd4 Bd6 13. g3 O-O 14. f3 Rc8 15. Be3 Nf8 16. Rac1 h5 17. Qd2 Rd8 18. Nce2 h4 19. Bg5 hxg3 20. Bxf6 gxf6 21. Qh6 Be5 22. Kh1 g2+ 23. Kxg2 Bxd4 24. Nxd4 Qe5 25. Kh1 Bxe4 26. Rg1+ Bg6 27. Nxe6 fxe6 28. Rxg6+ Nxg6 29. Qxg6+ Kf8 30. Qh6+ Ke7 31. Qh7+
